<div class="wrap ">
	<div class="content_wrap search">
		<%= render partial: 'schools/account_tab' %>

		<div class="search_header">
			<div class="title_bloc">
				<h1>Welcome to Boston Public Schools Registration</h1>
				<img class="logo_beta" src="/assets/logo_beta.png" alt="beta"/>
			</div>
			<p>This website provides resources for finding, exploring and comparing a student's eligible schools. </p>
							<p class="small_text tablet">Looking for the 2013-2014 school year?</p>
			
					 </div>
					<div class="search_section_content "> 
					 
						<!-- ADD CLASS "RIGHT" TO MOVE THE TODAY INDICATOR TO RIGHT OF THE TIME LINE, OR "LEFT" TO MOVE TO THE LEFT  FOR LARGEUR OF TABLET SIZE -->
						<!-- AND change the top % to ajust the today up or down -->
						<div class="today right" style="top:<%= timeline_percent(Date.today) %>;">
							<span aria-hidden="true" class="right icon-DBPS-Dev-Assets-SRG-30"></span>&nbsp; Today &nbsp;<span aria-hidden="true" class="left icon-DBPS-Dev-Assets-SRG-32"></span>
							<span class="yello_line"></span>
						</div> 
						<!-- END today indicator-->
						
						<!-- Discover section -->
			<section class="search_section first">
				<p class="small_text no_tablet">Looking for the 2013-2014 school year?</p>	
				<div class="content_left">
					
					<div class="logo discover" >
						<span aria-hidden="true" class="icon-DBPS-Dev-Assets-SRG-01"></span>
					</div>
					<div class="text">
						<br />
						<div class='bloc'>
							<p class='first'>
								As part of the registration process, every applicant is asked to complete a Home Language Survey. The results of this Survey determine whether a child needs additional language assessment at our Newcomers Assessment and Counseling Center. Results of the language assessment will indicate if a child should receive additional language learning support in school. If this is the case, a child's school choices may expand beyond his/her Home Based options to include program seats in a wider community cluster of schools. Click here to view a map of the ELL Clusters. Note, your cluster is based on your place of residence.  You may still use this tool to learn about your Home Based school options.
							</p>
							<p>
								For more information on clusters, the Language Assessment, or the Newcomer's Assessment and Counseling Center, please call a Welcome Center near you or contact the Newcomers Center directly at:
							</p>
						</div>
						<h2>617-635-1565</h2>

						<br />
						<br />
						<% if @student.iep_needs? %>
							<%= link_to 'Next', iep_needs_student_path(@student), id: 'next_button', class: 'orange_button' %>
						<% else %>
							<%= link_to 'Next', schools_path, id: 'next_button', class: 'orange_button' %>
						<% end %>
						<script>
							$('#next_button').click(function() {
								$('#next_button').text('Working...');
							});
						</script>
					</div>
				</div>
				<%= render partial: 'schools/vertical_timeline' %>
			</section>
			<!-- END Discover section -->
			
			<!-- REgister section -->
			<section class=" search_section second">
								
				<div class="content_left">
					<div class="logo register" >
						<span aria-hidden="true" class="icon-DBPS-Dev-Assets-SRG-02"></span>
					</div>
					<div class="text">
						<p>
							Once a student's list of schools has been chosen, registration begins by submitting the list and visiting a Welcome Center.
						</p>
						<a class="K" href="#" title="Learn more"  style="margin-bottom:0;">Learn more</a>
					</div>
				</div>
				<!-- timeline info of Register -->
				<div class="content_right">
					<span class="event" style="margin-bottom:39px;">
						<span class="desktop">
							 Jan 6<!--<span aria-hidden="true" class="icon-DBPS-Dev-Assets-SRG-35"></span>--><img class="point" src="/assets/red_point.png" /><br/>
